parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Driver's Side Door Locking Mechanism Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the driver's side door locking mechanism can cause the door to become permanently locked, making it difficult or impossible to exit the vehicle in an emergency, which can lead to accidents or fatalities.
symptoms: The door is permanently locked and cannot be opened from the outside handle or interior handle
the door is stuck in the locked position
unable to open the door from inside or outside
difficulty or inability to exit the vehicle in an emergency.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door handles can cause difficulty or inability to exit the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or fatalities in an emergency.
symptoms: The door handle breaks off
the door handle is stuck
unable to open the door from inside or outside
difficulty or inability to exit the vehicle in an emergency.
